NAME
    Log::ger::UseJSON - Use JSON::MaybeXS to dump data structures (as JSON)

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of Log::ger::UseJSON (from Perl
    distribution Log-ger-UseJSON), released on 2018-06-17.

SYNOPSIS
     use Log::ger::UseJSON;

    To configure:

     use Log::ger::UseJSON (clean=>0, pretty=>0);

DESCRIPTION
CONFIGURATION
  pretty
  clean
HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Log-ger-UseJSON>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Log-ger-UseJSON>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Log-ger-UseJSON>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

